Set of 8 Extensions, 4 CO Lines Automated Telephone System. This IKE-PBX system is an ideal telephone system for small offices and homes. It is very easy to install and use.
It has all the standard features comparable to those expensive PBX systems in the market. It works with your current analog phones and you do not need to spend extra money to buy proprietary telephones to work with the PBX

Our smart PABX 8 extensions intercoms system comes in full bundle with 6 pieces of Panasonic corded phones, a 300 meters installation cable, 6 pieces of intercom, flush sockets and 6 pieces of rj11 connectors and can be extended to 8 Phones. The smart PABX is already preprogrammed with calling numbers and ready for immediate operation after running the cables and socketing the display corded telephone boxes. However the device can be reprogrammed if you wish, for instance you are installing it in a hotel and you want to assign numbers based on room numbering.

Huawei GSM Table Phone ETS3125i FWP

A cellular device designed like a Land Phone and combines all the Features & Benefits of a Mobile Phone with that of a Land Phone to give you the best of the two worlds.

These features include FM Radio, Speakerphone function, SMS, CLIP/CLIR, phone lock, phone book, Clock, loud ringer, etc.

It works with all GSM Networks; MTN, Glo, Airtel, Etisalat, etc. Just insert SIM Cards of your choice networks and you are connected to start making and receiving calls.

It is ideal for Home, Office, and on the go. Ideal for keeping in touch with folks in the villa and home.

It is user friendly with large dial buttons and display. It comes with an external antenna to boost signal where GSM coverage is weak.

It comes with battery back up to ensure you remain connected even when the electricity goes off. Can use for VPN/CUG Free calls among branch office

Other Features:

Phone Book can store up to 200 contacts. Phone can autosave the last 20 dialed/received/missed numbers.

Supports call waiting. Has over 15 chords inbuilt music ringtones. Standby battery backup of up to 72hrs.

Windows 10 Pro (64 & 32 Bit DVD Included)
Windows® 10 Pro is the state-of-the-art operating system from Microsoft.

With Windows 10 Pro, you've got a great business partner. It has all the features of Windows 10 Home, plus important business functionality for encryption, remote log-in, creating virtual machines, and more. Get fast start-ups, a familiar yet expanded Start menu, and great new ways to get stuff done, plus innovative features like an all-new browser built for online action and Cortana, the more personal digital assistant. Windows 10 is not compatible with Windows Vista

Windows 10 is so familiar and easy to use, you'll feel like an expert. The Start Menu is back in an expanded form, plus we'll bring over your pinned apps and favorites so they're ready and waiting for you. It starts up and resumes fast, has more built-in security to help keep you safe, and is designed to work with software and hardware you already have. Windows 10 comes with Microsoft Edge, an all-new browser that's built to give you a better web experience. Write2 or type notes directly on web pages and share them with others, read online articles free of distraction, and save your favorite reads for later access. And with Cortana3 enabled, you get instant access to key actions-like making reservations or reading reviews-without leaving the page you're on. Easily snap up to four apps in place and see all open tasks in a single view. You can even create virtual desktops when you need more space or want to group things by the project. Windows 10 enables your apps to look and work great in all modes, on all devices. On 2-in-1 devices, your screen can be optimized to work with touch or keyboard and mouse

Cortana
Cortana is your truly personal digital assistant who works across all your Windows 10 devices to help you get things done. By learning more about you over time, Cortana becomes more useful every day, staying transparent and keeping your trust.

System Requirements
Here's what Microsoft says you need to run Windows 10: Processor: 1 gigahertz (GHz) or faster. RAM: 1 gigabyte (GB) (32-bit) or 2 GB (64-bit) Free hard disk space: 16 GB. Graphics card: Microsoft DirectX 9 graphics device with WDDM driver. A Microsoft account and Internet access.
